718453f-c.title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 68th Street
718453f-c.text:
(1)
Second Church of Christ Scientist, Central Park West at the S.W. corner of 68th Street. At the left may be seen a portion of a new apartment building under construction on the former site of the
gNown House Apartments.
March 11, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, showing more of Central Park West.
November 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
(3)
The same, showing the side view of the church on 68th Street.
March 11, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
